{"tid":370900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中國領導人) 習近平點名大讚《打死不離3父女》","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T10:31:26.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f16de47b0232f7a26537a70f00e63788f8b517c0","tid":370900,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"習近平點名大讚《打死不離3父女》, 並希望更多類似電影在中國上映.<br />\n<br />\n《打死不離3父女》明天香港上映.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinafilminsider.com/xi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinafilminsider.com%2Fxi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china%2F&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cc186821\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinafilminsider.com/xi-jinping-tells-modi-loves-dangal-want-movies-china/</a><br />\n<br />\nBollywood&rsquo;s Dangal, already the highest earning non-Hollywood foreign film in Chinese history, earned another important Chinese fan over the weekend &mdash; China&rsquo;s President Xi Jinping.<br />\n<br />\nSpeaking to his Indian counterpart Prime Minister Narendra Modi at a summit in Kazakhstan on Friday, Xi said he &lsquo;loved&rsquo; the Aamir Khan-starrer, and that he wanted to see more such movies in China in the future, India&rsquo;s Foreign Secretary S Jaishankar told Indian media."},{"pid":"514b2361b0b21518ecac7512a60d34dabfd9817e","tid":370900,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe10121d79102299de8a8ee20820f07c717dc30e","tid":370900,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"打死不離3父女 - 預告片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/fNX7Q5sHKaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfNX7Q5sHKaI&d=ox5U%2F7G%2FhUOIrXJuGdZiwEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f53c1b6e\" target=\"_blank\">ht